track.name: 'Round Midnight
comments: Monk was a genius and I have always loved his music.
break it down monk, what a genius
a true jazz mystic, when he played he definitely brought you places.
off the charted depths and navigating masterfully that box of magic hammers to produce a syncopated, hip, tipsy, modal jazz before any one knew such a thing could exist.....
Bewitching piano deep pure playful and crazy as ever. That's in another sphere of sensibility and awareness from Thelonious
Ah, bless Monk... So deep, pure, playful, funky.
Solo piano version this time, magical.
